Package org.cpnsim.datacenter

Class InstanceGroupQueueFifo

java.lang.Object
org.cpnsim.datacenter.InstanceGroupQueueFifo
All Implemented Interfaces:
InstanceGroupQueue
public class InstanceGroupQueueFifo extends Object implements InstanceGroupQueue
A class to represent a instanceGroup queue with first in first out. This class implements the interface InstanceGroupQueue.
Since:
LGDCloudSim 1.0
Author:
Jiawen Liu
